{"tid":2300791,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"根本依家mac就係弱勢,如果唔係就唔洗千方百計想痴windows嚟用啦","createTime":"2020-11-25T21:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T13:07:57.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"559272ebbf31613a46585a9f3faa0131c7106ed6","tid":2300791,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T21:45:16.000Z","msg":"啲人成日話蘋果唔想出macipad混合機,因為想分開兩條線賺多啲錢,其實蘋果不知幾想出部咁嘅野嚟谷mac啦,不過技術問題出唔到咁解,更何況ipad都係弱勢同iphone比,所以先出部垃圾iphone嚟谷ipad<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nmac咁強勢就唔洗千方百計想痴windows嚟用啦,又唔見ios裝置可以容許裝android ,arm mac想裝windows但微軟唔show佢，搞到要痴ios啲app嚟用咁cheap<br />\n蘋果高層談Windows在M1 mac機可能性  竟把責任推俾微軟？<br />\n很多mac用家可能因為本身是學生又或工作需要，都會加裝Windows。如今mac機使用M1晶片，ARM架構下無法再安裝一般為Intel架構而設的Windows操作系統。其實，微軟本身已經有Windows on ARM版本，那麼為什麼M1晶片的新mac機不能安裝這個版本？又為什麼蘋果的Boot Camp工具，只支援Intel mac安裝Windows操作系統？<br />\n<br />\n外國傳媒Ars訪問蘋果高層Craig Federighi時，Craig提到目前mac機技術上可以行到Windows on ARM，但目前Windows on ARM版本授權，只能配合預先安裝在機中的情況，Craig稱要微軟把有關授權技術，支援mac機合法安裝Windows on ARM才可。他強調，mac絕對行到Windows on ARM。<br />\n<br />\n他在訪問中提到，其實目前已有一些為M1 mac機而設的方案，可以行到Windows apps，例如我們早前提過的CrossOver便是"},{"pid":"209612253d8003bd685795d2ce7554ab5faa1614","tid":2300791,"uid":343977,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T22:34:32.000Z","msg":"蘋果做生意駛你條柒頭教咩？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1ccda18cc131146237bde21f525373d38b60b5","tid":2300791,"uid":116910,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T22:41:05.000Z","msg":"其實樓豬講乜尻 有冇人可以翻譯下"},{"pid":"4bf602d0d7c5f5201fe8331b250d71ecf345a9ed","tid":2300791,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"209612253d8003bd685795d2ce7554ab5faa1614","tid":2300791,"uid":343977,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T22:34:32.000Z","msg":"蘋果做生意駛你條柒頭教咩？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T22:55:55.000Z","msg":"我邊有教佢做生意？佢做生意好成功喎，我只係講出佢唔及windows嘅事實，mac賺錢唔等於勁，軟件廢到無論"},{"pid":"17c69dab96be335ea1159bfc8001ca4ae24ec5c8","tid":2300791,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"5c1ccda18cc131146237bde21f525373d38b60b5","tid":2300791,"uid":116910,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T22:41:05.000Z","msg":"其實樓豬講乜尻 有冇人可以翻譯下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T22:57:22.000Z","msg":"反駁某人話mac同ipad唔合體係因為想賺多一水，事實係技術上根本唔得"},{"pid":"4748e7a4e543c5a98dcef56dc320953dd552ea4e","tid":2300791,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T22:57:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>蘋果做生意駛你條柒頭教咩？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>我邊有教佢做生意？佢做生意好成功喎，我只係講出佢唔及windows嘅事實，mac賺錢<span class=\"red\">多過windows</span>唔等於勁，軟件廢到無論</blockquote>"},{"pid":"69f36fd70dc7184cca7616af4f54d69ecdff0255","tid":2300791,"uid":19725,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T00:06:54.000Z","msg":"樓主公屋windows android 窮鬼黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e5f123974dc37ebae5cfae43fcf251cb1a22c5","tid":2300791,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T05:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20aa4bf4893f5b02cc27dbdfe045bf7f3438a2f2","tid":2300791,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T12:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde2a7b784e1fd4e8eaadc9b3b2954a3efbf9a7c","tid":2300791,"uid":98796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T13:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />差唔多有10年無用windows..."},{"pid":"65af69644ab297ea666f13d93664c02f8181eddc","tid":2300791,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69f36fd70dc7184cca7616af4f54d69ecdff0255","tid":2300791,